1. "commander" command line parsing
2. automatically launch temporary postgres server
3. fix view caching/checking
4. "hold" system for blocking/releasing updates when promise is running async
5. Connection wrapper object (query, queryOne, queryOneOrNone)
6. insert DSL
      insertOne(conn, "employee",
          {
              fname: sql`${"alice"}`,
              lname: sql`fname || ${"johnson"}`
          }, sql`RETURNING id`);

      insertMany(conn, "employee",
          [{
              id: sql`${}`,
              fname: sql`${}`,
              lname: sql`${fname} || fname`
          }], sql`RETURNING id`);
